nodes.text: Bongo Bays were buildings where Gungans got their bongos repaired. The bays also sold bongo fuel that was made from fermented bubble wort. In 32 BBY, the Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi and Qui-Gon Jinn took their donated tribubble bongo from the Bongo Bay along with their navigator, the Gungan Jar Jar Binks.
